      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRUTAL EDGE (6) still a maiden after seven runs but rarely out of the placings. Was in the placings again last time finishing third (18.92) at this track. Speedy beginner who can find the front despite the tricky draw. Can go on with it. MINI AURORA (8) comes off a moderate effort last start, finishing fifth at this track over 320m behind Cawbourne Tiff (18.86). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. TELL ME WRONG (7) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at this track over 320m behind Cheeky Edge (19.74) in a Maiden. Placed at his previous run. Deserves plenty of respect. BRACKEN RAVEN (1) makes debut for the Christopher Newcombe kennel. Drawn well and should get her chance. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
